Main content:
- Analyze the workflow of an e-commerce platform: product listing, cart management, payment, and order fulfillment.
- Compare Amazon’s e-commerce model with another major platform eBay.
- Understand how cloud computing supports scalability and efficiency in e-commerce.
- Explore how Amazon Web Services (AWS) powers Amazon’s backend operations.
- Learn how online payments are processed securely.
- Investigate the role of recommendation algorithms in personalizing the user experience.
